T1  - An Upperbound Algorithm for the Single and Multiple Terminal Delivery Problem
AU  - Tillman, Frank A.
AU  - Cain, Thomas M.
Y1  - 1972/07/01
PY  - 1972
DA  - 1972/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.18.11.664
